fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize = (20, 6))

marvel_counts = marvel_df["ALIGN"].value_counts()
marvel_explode = (0, 0, 0.1)
marvel_colors = ['#FF5733', '#33FF57', '#3357FF']
marvel_labels = marvel_counts.index

dc_counts = dc_df["ALIGN"].value_counts()
dc_explode = (0, 0, 0.05, 0.1)
dc_colors = ["#FF69B4", "#FFD700", "#7B68EE", "#FF4500"]
dc_labels = dc_counts.index

axs[0].pie(marvel_counts, explode = marvel_explode, labels = marvel_labels, colors = marvel_colors, autopct = '%1.3f%%', textprops = {'fontsize': 12})
axs[0].set_title('Marvel Characters', fontsize = 14, weight = 'bold', color = '#2F0F5D')
axs[0].legend(loc = "upper left")

axs[1].pie(dc_counts, explode = dc_explode, labels = dc_labels, colors = dc_colors, autopct = '%1.3f%%', textprops = {'fontsize': 12})
axs[1].set_title('DC Characters', fontsize = 14, weight = 'bold', color = '#2F0F5D')
axs[1].legend(loc = "upper left")

axs[0].set_aspect('equal')
axs[1].set_aspect('equal')
